A New theme for this app! Yes we are super happy to announce that we have enhanced entire user flow experience in a fresh and beautiful interface layout for this app. What s New: 1 Recorder Powerful audio voice recorder with high quality. 2 Recordings Manage recordings in one place. Group recording using the Playlist. 3 Cloud Import Export recording or audio files to Google Drive Dropbox cloud and more. 4 Setting Protect files using PASSCODE Now you can set totally new various themes. Experience the new theme and let us know how it works! We hope you like it.
